Class AbstractNumberOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.block.panel.block.AbstractBlock

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    SumOperation

    public class AbstractNumberOperation
extends AbstractBlock
implements Block.ParameterInsertBlock, Block.ValueBlock<java.lang.Number>
    The basic Block implementation for all number operations. All methods are implemented for block including code and paint.
